<item>
            <title>[LU-20106] changelog delay on MTIME evengt</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-20106</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;changelog record for an object_fid for MTIME does not show up in lustre changelog&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;2026-04-08 15:55:21,352&lt;/b&gt; mdt=lustre-MDT0000 event_id=22067 event_time_secs=1775685321 event_type=MTIME event_timestamp=2026-04-08T21:55:21.208626 parent_fid=0x200000402:0x124a:0x0 object_fid=0x200000402:0x124c:0x0 source_parent_fid=- source_object_fid=- status=stored raw=llapi record #22067&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;making one change to one file the changelog record is not reported for several minutes&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;*2026-04-08 15:58:03,711 *mdt=lustre-MDT0000 event_id=22068 event_time_secs=1775685483 event_type=MTIME event_timestamp=2026-04-08T21:58:03.649668 parent_fid=0x200000402:0x124a:0x0 object_fid=0x200000402:0x124c:0x0 source_parent_fid=- source_object_fid=- status=stored raw=llapi record #22068&lt;/p&gt;</description>
